ii desu ka
by Kansha » Fri 02.19.2010 10:00 am My last Nihongo class for basic romaji 1.Senshu no doyobi Nihongo kurasu owarimashita. Watashi tachi wa shiken o torimashita. Muzukashi desu ga tanoshii desu. (i passed the exam that's why i was happy <- Nihongo de nan desu ka ) Rasuto shiken o owarimashita, sore kare watachi tachi wa "Komoro Soba" resutoran de bangohan o tabemashita. sempai ni furi bangohan o moraimashita kara totemo yokatta deshita ( <- i was planning to say "our classmate treated us free dinner that's why i was very happy ) Tempura ya ramen nado ga arimashita. Totemo oishii desu soshite takakunai desu. Later on, i had to say goodbye to my classmates and to my teacher as i had to meet my boyfriend to watch a movie (Nihongo de nan desu ka )**OPEN TO ALL CORRECTIONS**Arigatou Gozaimashita. Gambarimasho! Kansha
