Re: ii desu ka
by UkiUki88 » Sun 02.21.2010 7:01 am Also, for the last sentence, you could say it two ways.1. Ato de kareshi to issho ni eiga o mi ni iku kara sensei to tomodachi to owakare shimashita. => This means you said farewell to your friends and teachers. Eiga o mi ni iku => To go and watch a movieYou could also say you left early instead of saying goodbye.2. Ato de kareshi to issho ni eiga o mi ni iku kara hayaku ikanakereba narimasen deshita. => This means you had to leave early.
