Re: ii desu ka
by samtsco » Sat 08.28.2010 12:58 am Ok, I looked it up and it seems that TAME without the NI can mean a few different things, but in my case, it means AS A RESULT OF instead of BECAUSE. Subtle difference there. Add the NI and you get IN ORDER TO.
